        <subsection xml:id="subsec-logical-equivalence">
          <title>
            Logical Equivalence
          </title>
          <p>
            Two logical expressions are said to be <term>logically equivalent</term> if they have the same values in their columns in the truth table.
            <idx><h>logical equivalence</h><h>of propositions</h></idx>
            <idx><h>equivalence, logical</h><h>of propositions</h></idx>
