          </p>
        </subsection>
        <subsection xml:id="ssec-alt-conditional">
          <title>
            The <q>or</q> form of the Conditional
          </title>
          <p>
            The conditional <m>\conditional</m> can be rewritten in an alternate form in terms of the basic connectives.
            <idx><h>conditional</h><h><q>or</q> form</h></idx>
            <idx><em>or</em> form of conditional</idx>
            Consider the truth table below:
            <tabular halign="center" top="major" left="medium">
              <row bottom="medium">
                <cell left="medium" right="medium">
                         <m>p</m>
                </cell>
                <cell right="medium">
                  <m>q</m>
                </cell>
                <cell right="medium">
