                <m>\sum\limits_{j = 4}^{10} {{{\left( { - 1} \right)}^j}}  = 1 + \left( { - 1} \right) + 1 + \left( { - 1} \right) + 1 + \left( { - 1} \right) + 1 = 1</m>
